      public org.apache.uima.collection.CollectionReader createReader​(java.lang.String[] pArgs)

      Parameters:
      pArgs - relies upon the argument --inputFormat= with the values coming from FrameworkBaselineApplicaiton.TEXT_READER_ ....
      Returns:
      CollectionReader

    • createReader

      public org.apache.uima.collection.CollectionReader createReader​(int pReaderType, java.lang.String[] args)
